                In no way affiliated with, or endorsed by <a href="https://www.worldclimbing.com/">WoRLd CLiMbiNg</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-10">
            <a class="text-[#C0C7D1] hover:text-primary transition-colors font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] text-xs uppercase tracking-widest" href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a class="text-[#C0C7D1] hover:text-primary transition-colors font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] text-xs uppercase tracking-widest" href="/faq/">FAQ</a>
